Tunggu!

811
01:20:04,867 --> 01:20:06,461
Tembak!

812
01:20:11,624 --> 01:20:13,329
Aku mahu dia!

813
01:20:15,173 --> 01:20:16,474
Dia!

814
01:20:17,509 --> 01:20:18,810
Dia!

815
01:20:25,850 --> 01:20:27,701
- Dan dia!
- Baik, tuan.

816
01:20:27,702 --> 01:20:29,656
Kamu dengar arahan.
Bawa mereka naik.

817
01:20:29,681 --> 01:20:31,469
Bagaimana dengan yang ini?

818
01:20:32,107 --> 01:20:34,099
Tinggalkan kanak-kanak.

819
01:20:40,289 --> 01:20:42,639
- Apa kita patut buat?
- Diam.

820
01:20:43,369 --> 01:20:46,515
X-Ray 7, aku membuat pemeriksaan terakhir.

821
01:20:53,915 --> 01:20:55,927
Baiklah, bawa mereka naik!

822
01:20:55,952 --> 01:20:57,462
Kosong!

823
01:21:03,039 --> 01:21:04,625
Terima kasih, Jean.

824
01:21:05,061 --> 01:21:06,282
Kita kena bantu mereka.

825
01:21:06,307 --> 01:21:08,852
- Kurt, boleh bawa kita ke sana?
- Kau nak masuk ke sana?

826
01:21:08,884 --> 01:21:10,100
Bagaimana kalau mereka nampak kita?

827
01:21:10,125 --> 01:21:12,745
Jangan risau. Mereka takkan
nampak kita, percayalah.

828
01:21:14,766 --> 01:21:16,259
Pegang erat.

829
01:21:31,495 --> 01:21:33,536
Kurt, keluarkan kita!

830
01:21:35,412 --> 01:21:36,452
Tak boleh!

831
01:21:36,477 --> 01:21:40,155
Sebaik sahaja mereka tutup pintu,
seolah-olah ada medan eletrik.

832
01:21:40,180 --> 01:21:42,339
- Sama seperti di Berlin.
- Jean, masuki fikiran juruterbang.

833
01:21:42,364 --> 01:21:43,823
- Jangan biar mereka lari!
- Tak boleh.

834
01:21:43,848 --> 01:21:47,059
Aku tak dapat mencapai juruterbang.
Aku tak dapat mencapai sesiapa pun.

835
01:21:54,143 --> 01:21:56,283
<i>Kami turut menerima laporan
dari Eropah dan Asia.</i>

836
01:21:56,308 --> 01:21:58,537
<i>Ini bukan sekadar
fenomena Amerika Syarikat.</i>

837
01:21:58,562 --> 01:22:02,429
<i>Nampaknya seluruh dunia
melucutkan senjata nuklear mereka.</i>

838
01:22:02,430 --> 01:22:05,257
<i>Pentagon telah mengesahkan
pelancaran nuklear dari Rusia,...</i>

839
01:22:05,282 --> 01:22:07,326
<i>...UK, Israel dan China.</i>

840
